{"tid":1962908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捧紅《老夫子》《YES！》 ，98歲香港出版界巨人吳中興逝世","createTime":"2020-04-07T18:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:00:30.000Z","uid":35221,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7bb2a5b3942e2ec23f10d891afc80c0f5a94a4","tid":1962908,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"捧紅《老夫子》《YES！》 98歲出版界巨人吳中興逝世<br />\n20200407<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/OP8rI7l5kWkicfeThlaPHDy1PQo=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/EKMA5EGWS3E7FDX2SCML4I4WNI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FOP8rI7l5kWkicfeThlaPHDy1PQo%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FEKMA5EGWS3E7FDX2SCML4I4WNI.png&h=1854ded5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李家皓攝；小圖譚宇正facebook圖片<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n本地漫畫經典《老夫子》的出版人吳中興近日逝世，享年98歲。吳中興從事出版及發行超過半世紀，由他管理的「吳興記書報社」於1954年創辦，60年代起成為發行業「龍頭」之一，見證出版業的盛衰。不少書迷得知消息後，紛紛在社交網站上悼念這位香港出版界巨人，感激吳的貢獻令廣大讀者有好書相伴。<br />\n<br />\n「賀老夫子50年香港畫板」籌劃人譚宇正，昨日（6日）於社交網站貼文，證實吳中興近日逝世，並憶述二人於書展的新書推介會上認識，永遠懷念這位香港出版界巨人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/i_WR4p9fvUx4hbnFrwApl6sKpf8=/802x534/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/YII3VC365KEUOE4LXKEOHR47TU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fi_WR4p9fvUx4hbnFrwApl6sKpf8%3D%2F802x534%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FYII3VC365KEUOE4LXKEOHR47TU.png&h=84abb848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李家皓攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n譚引述吳興記出版社余經理表示，上周五吳中興在位於上環樂古道的辦公室，中午突然說腳不舒服，他立即送吳到醫院。因年事已高，至周一（6日）吳因心臟衰竭，在醫院仙逝，走的很安詳。<br />\n<br />\n據知，吳中興的孩子散居世界各地，這些年來一直都是經理伉儷就近細心照顧，吳在醫院離世時，經理及她孫女等人，還有家傭都在旁。<br />\n<br />\n譚亦引述，老夫子第二代作者王澤老師稱，敬悼吳伯伯，「吳老先生從1964年出版《老夫子》至今，也感念吳老先生對我們的厚愛和照顧，願吳伯伯安息！」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200407/large/1586274679_1e51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586274679_1e51.jpg&h=fd76e276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著名漫畫家馬龍於2013年替吳中興繪畫畫像，慶祝91歲大壽。（譚宇正提供相片）<br />\n<br />\n主動與王澤接洽合作<br />\n<br />\n吳中興與《老夫子》結下不解之緣56年。他生前接受訪問時指，於1964年在《星島晚報》看到老王澤的連載漫畫，認為其畫功佳且內容幽默，憑着11年發行經驗主動洽談合作。他指，看中《老夫子》人物造型特別趣怪，穿着晚清馬褂服飾，加上作品主題與基層文化貼近，能引起大眾共鳴。結果第一冊6,000本兩天內賣光，他回憶，當時印「老夫子」漫畫，好像印鈔票一樣。<br />\n<br />\n時移勢易，吳中興亦主動提出改革《老夫子》。因應90年代末雜誌選擇多，隨着發售點增多，便利店開始賣書，《老夫子》便由原本約A4大小改版為「書仔」，開創了新型銷售運作模式。「老夫子」從一冊港幣六毛錢至售價逾數十元，吳功不可沒。<br />\n<br />\n「吳興記」除了出版《老夫子》，亦曾力捧青少年娛樂雜誌《YES！》，於90年代風靡一時。作家沈西城曾撰文，讚揚吳「生意經頂呱呱，算盤一撥，萬人莫敵&hellip;&hellip;幾乎叫得出名頭的雜誌，或多或少跟吳老闆沾上邊」。沈又指，吳為人精明、果斷，只要認為作家有本事、名氣，便一挺胸：「包在咱身上」。<br />\n<br />\n吳興記書報社於上環樂古道設有門市，並轉型為老夫子精品的專賣店，售賣《老夫子》漫畫、模型和公仔等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/sWaGrZS12YonrAN1AScyc-1MotM=/802x534/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/F5Z557BJ6WRY32SC2TO5JSJYJI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FsWaGrZS12YonrAN1AScyc-1MotM%3D%2F802x534%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FF5Z557BJ6WRY32SC2TO5JSJYJI.png&h=ad4502c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳興記書報社放着《老夫子》的擺設。李家皓攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200407/H3EGK37YQWTJ3HHDO2YFEMID5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200407%2FH3EGK37YQWTJ3HHDO2YFEMID5Q%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpAcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=1fc7d2eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200407%2FH3EGK37YQWTJ3HHDO2YFEMID5Q%2F&h=d6a894d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200407/H3EGK37YQWTJ3HHDO2YFEMID5Q/</a>"},{"pid":"286782f59451bfc22fbdbf8c61d2b13705cc9831","tid":1962908,"uid":185092,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"睇老夫子應該聽過吳興記"},{"pid":"1e31b2908168cdaedbf4409187288039485b5884","tid":1962908,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"286782f59451bfc22fbdbf8c61d2b13705cc9831","tid":1962908,"uid":185092,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"睇老夫子應該聽過吳興記"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T19:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59f6946786ab56bebe031f953fcd47ff60e6298","tid":1962908,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T22:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dccf64487d74796ad64aceb74dc9144bd4c014","tid":1962908,"uid":59920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T23:02:20.000Z","msg":"個地鋪不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37754def1291116d3100affb8a2444e894d8e374","tid":1962908,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T00:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dad61ee8f3445321ee59cb3ff795969cc02ba22","tid":1962908,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68955826052725a9f486601ba4ddadd17940fbc","tid":1962908,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好怕大家忘記了，可唔可以入嚟幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［5個月］［整合］大家記唔記得今日係咩日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區